cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the hardware log level to an invalid enum 'debug_invalid' will cause logging configuration errors and prevent proper log initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將硬體日誌等級設定為無效的枚舉值 'debug_invalid'，會導致日誌配置錯誤，並阻止正確的日誌初始化。
